Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.49,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.65,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:53.40,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.21,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.35,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:22.70,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:27.43,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.43,0:01:34.37,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep the hell out of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't eat! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.35,0:02:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The main clause, "I heard..." is in the past tense,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the subordinate clause is in the past tense also.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.97,0:02:39.17,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Then Ruland picked up the scythe and created with it a circular space,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:44.78,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,...three or four yards in diameter, just for the insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:51.05,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Then he told Jupiter to let the string go, and come down from the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. My eraser...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we eating too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, we're growing, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I just worry about growing sideways...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.09,0:03:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She's probably eating lunch alone somewhere. Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,10. Mariko
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Finished with lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko, what do you want for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, like I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's been three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a steak?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,With lots of French fries! Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I don't want anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see how unhappy this makes me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please eat something. For my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You are all that is precious in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't anything else for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Mariko? Won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"Please", "please"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you say anything but "please"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Get angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Being like that is what made my father... made him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... "confusion"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the synonym of "confusion"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A page is missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, what am I doing with this cheap dictionary?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,May I come in, Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been studying so hard lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you know mid-terms are coming soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. A reward for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:05:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! An English-to-English dictionary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So... "confusion"... "confusion"...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know I needed a new dictionary?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He was watching you study in the living room the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Thank you, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a dessert for you. Keep up the good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I made your favorite... apple pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I am surrounded by the warmth of my father's love, and my mother's too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize how happy I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I care how they met.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...I just don't understand about Mariko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Call again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My first section is Physics, rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine is English.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, sheesh, you're really working hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. I have a new dictionary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mona-Lisa-no-Kimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh good! Fukiko-sama has a favor to ask of you both...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So! See you at lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you bring flowers for the tea ceremony today,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,From the College Union?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Flowers for a tea ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We will rely on your good taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-san, you seem reluctant?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you would be so kind, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sorority holds a tea ceremony once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Afterwards they discuss upcoming events and such...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,These ceremonies are so important!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To think we'd be chosen to select the flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What an honor it is! It's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,About the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-san, I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A Tea Ceremony? What an elegant life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So then? You two picked the flowers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right about that birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Something happened, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. If you can't talk about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's one for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.02,0:10:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So skinny! You're wasting your natural beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.69,0:10:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't go on abusing your health this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What good is health? Who cares about health!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't say that if you weren't still healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-no-Kimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.99,0:10:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...you just don't understand how I feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see just a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always been adored by so many... Can't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow, I want a hug from Kaoru-no-Kimi too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet down and get ready for sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:35.59,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you warmed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.52,0:11:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Misonoo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok! Are you ready to take a serve?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no... Her serve is so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She's such an athlete!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Heads up! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.92,0:12:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My nap was interrupted by your ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It figures, that it was you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:12:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei, throw the ball back, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come up instead of playing with this stupid ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The view from here is splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything looks small and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Even people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Orihara Kaoru looks small too. From here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the nonsense, come down. I'll let you join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be a pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.18,0:13:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei! Throw the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei! Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.17,0:14:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Back with it, everyone. Don't bother with this lazybones!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.39,0:15:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.66,0:15:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! To the nurse's office!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you coming with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about her. My god!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! And she's unconscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't reach her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go to her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Her mom might still be out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait for her in front...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:16:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's best for her to be told in person, because of the shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help her as much as I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.70,0:16:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...because despite everything, she is my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take your bag home for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! That will help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Hospitalized?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Orihara-san just called to tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She needs to stay in the hospital for a couple of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's not that serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They say it's anemia and malnutrition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Malnutrition?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you talk to her mother yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Abusing her precious life like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,These kids... how could they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu-san suffering from malnutrition?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Malnutrition? How could that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-san! You've come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.86,0:18:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me but... Mariko-san has fainted!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko... fainted!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What! Mariko stopped eating because of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't eat until you forgive her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No more than a sip of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no... Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Shinobu-san asking for... forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.24,0:19:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She wanted to wait as long as it took until you forgave her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...of your own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know. I had no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There was nothing I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd made up my mind to force her to eat something today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She probably was hoping I would. I finally realized that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.95,0:19:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san... Mariko-san was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all because of me... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-no-Kimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You've stayed with me all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother will be here soon, Misonoo-san, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevermind. Put an end to this foolishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you? Are you really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko, Nanako-san is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I don't need you. I have a lot of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.09,0:21:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.91,0:21:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I missed saying goodbye to Kaoru-no-Kimi, because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... as for you, you aren't my only friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.79,0:21:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My life is completely full... of so many friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.05,0:22:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,To forgive her, or not to forgive her...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.33,0:22:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who am I to be so judgmental or presumptuous?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.47,0:23:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The school called my publishing company...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.74,0:23:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.08,0:23:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san is facing loneliness, and her own self, head on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.35,0:23:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were me, I'd try to ignore it or try to avoid it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.09,0:23:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She's 16, same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.76,0:23:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a 16-year old hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.01,0:24:14.21,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.21,0:24:19.68,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.15,0:24:25.29,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.29,0:24:30.76,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.50,0:24:37.04,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.04,0:24:42.51,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.51,0:24:45.24,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.24,0:24:48.05,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.05,0:24:50.45,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.45,0:24:55.72,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.93,0:25:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,While waiting for Fukiko in a heavy rainstorm under an elm tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.96,0:25:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei gets a high fever and collapses.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.20,0:25:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When Nanako takes Rei to her apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.49,0:25:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...she is shocked to find the room filled with mirrors!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.01,0:25:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: Under the Elm Tree
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.62,0:25:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
